"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:4.4.9\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">4.4.9</span> 標題：香碟（incense dish）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： כַּף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kaf)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:29\">EXO 25:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:16\">EXO 37:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:7\">NUM 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:14\">NUM 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:20\">NUM 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:26\">NUM 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:32\">NUM 7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:38\">NUM 7:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:44\">NUM 7:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:50\">NUM 7:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:56\">NUM 7:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:62\">NUM 7:62</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:68\">NUM 7:68</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:74\">NUM 7:74</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:80\">NUM 7:80</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:84\">NUM 7:84</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:86\">NUM 7:86</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:86\">NUM 7:86</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:86\">NUM 7:86</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:50\">1KI 7:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:14\">2KI 25:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:22\">2CH 4:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:14\">2CH 24:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:18\">JER 52:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:19\">JER 52:19</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>香碟是帳幕和聖殿中盛香的器具，很可能只用來盛香，並不在裡面燒香，所以不應和香爐混淆。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯來文<em>kaf</em> 字面意為「手」，特指手掌（有時指腳掌）。大多數譯本和解經家認為，<em>kaf</em> 在上面所列的經文中是指香碟。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:0\">NUM 7:0</a> 特別將<em>kaf</em> 和香聯繫起來。有些譯本選擇用「香」一詞來限定<em>kaf</em> 的翻譯；例如，在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:7\">NUM 4:7</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> 譯作“dishes for incense”（「香盤」），<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 譯作“incense bowls”（「香碗」）。</p>\n<p>鍋、盆、罐、壺：參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">5.12 鍋、盆、罐、壺 (cooking pot, kettle)&lt;REALIA:5.12&gt;</a> 。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
